{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_03_02",
  "title": "kana 2話 もっといい場所連れてけよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌のグラビア撮影と取材ねぇ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A magazine photo shoot and interview‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9333332777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……怒ってないみたいだ。この間は）\n（少し失礼なことを言ったかもしれないからな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…She doesn't seem angry.）\n（I might have said something a bit rude last time.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5436216649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、テーマは『大人の恋愛』\n先方から、ぜひkanaさんにって依頼がきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ the theme is \"Adult Romance.\"\nWe received a request specifically asking for you‚ kana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛特集……また？　何百回やってんの？\nったく、どいつもこいつも恋愛好き過ぎじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Another romance feature…? How many times has this been done?\nSeriously‚ why is everyone so obsessed with romance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしやりたくないようなら、断っても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't want to do it‚ we can always decline…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333332777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "やるって。今はBIG4だった時みたいに\n仕事選んでる立場じゃないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll do it. I'm not in a position to be picking and\nchoosing jobs like when we were the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃーんと読者の期待に応えてみせるって\n今まで通りにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll make sure to meet the readers' expectations‚\nas always.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\n先方と調整しておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Understood.\nI'll coordinate with them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "何？　その不満そうな顔\n言いたいことあるなら、はっきり言えば？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with that discontented look?\nIf you have something to say‚ say it clearly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ……先日はkanaさんの仕事のスタイルに\n踏み込み過ぎてしまって、すみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no… I just felt like I may have intruded on your\nwork style the other day‚ kana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺はどちらがいいとか\nそういうことが言いたかった訳ではなく――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not trying to say which is better\nor anything like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0333315531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あーもう、うっさいうっさい\n分かってるから。で、どんな恋愛特集なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ enough already.\nI get it. So‚ what's this romance feature about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0666704813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今回のテーマは『大人の恋愛』です\n掲載誌も、今までのティーン誌とは違って大人向けです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The theme this time is \"Adult Romance.\"\nThe magazine is also aimed at adults‚ not teenagers like before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8000038146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん。今までとターゲット層が違うってことね\nじゃあ、受け答えも少し変えなきゃだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm. So‚ the target audience is different from before.\nGuess I'll have to adjust my responses a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3000038146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。でも、この企画がうまくいけば\nティーンの子達からの憧れだけではなく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. But if this project goes well‚\nI think it could lead to not only admiration from teenagers",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7333340961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "同年代の共感とか新しいファン層の獲得にも\n繋がると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but also empathy from people our age and\nthe acquisition of new fan demographics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1249216514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "同年代の共感……か……\nポンコツにしては悪くないじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Empathy from people our age‚ huh…\nNot bad for a scatterbrain like you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、フツーの女の子達が\nこんな可愛いkanaに共感なんて出来るかなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But seriously‚ can ordinary girls really relate to\nsomeone as cute as me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "外見だけじゃなく、内面にも興味はありますよ\nたとえばkanaさんの新しい一面を見せてあげるとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're interested not just in looks but also in your inner self.\nFor example‚ showing a new side of yourself‚ kana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "出た。どうせ素を見せろとか言うんでしょ？\nほんと好きだよね、そういうの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There it is. You're gonna ask to show the real me‚ right?\nYou really love that kind of thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9000007628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あー、やだやだ\n素こそが正義だと思っちゃってる感じ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I can't stand it.\nYou're all so obsessed with the idea that being genuine is everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい。そこまでは言ってないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please wait. I didn't say all that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5000007072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "言ってなくても分かるっつーの\nそういうのが好きなやつらがいるのも知ってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you didn't say it‚ I know.\nThere are people who love that kind of stuff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7000007628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そういうやつに限って、人の素を見たがるのに\n思ってたのと違う～って勝手に失望するんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But those people‚ especially‚ get disappointed when they see\nthe real person‚ and it's not what they expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "あいつらが見たいのは本当のkanaの素じゃなくて\n自分の理想とするkanaの素だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What they want to see isn't the real kana‚\nbut their idealized version of kana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.5666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどです……\nいろんな経験をされてきたんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nYou've had various experiences‚ haven't you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6333340961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？\nちょっと、何勝手に想像してんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?\nHey‚ what are you imagining on your own?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4666674295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "その少し憐れむみたいな目、マジうざいんですけど！\nこれは恋愛に限った話じゃないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That slightly pitying look is seriously annoying!\nThis isn't just about romance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.5333340961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……じゃあkanaさんの恋愛観って\nどんな感じなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So what's your view on romance‚\nkana-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.5333340961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}に話す必要なくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I really need to tell you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.3666673738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
